# Helm Chart
- easy way to may dynamic parameters accross the yaml's

1. It requires a file called "values.yml"
2. We need to change configurable properties with "{{.values.property}}"

# Commands from Hub

> Search keyword from Hub
helm search hub <KEYWORD>

> Install repo
helm repo add bitnami https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami

> Search from Repo
helm search repo <KEYWORD>

> Find all helm repo
helm repo list

> install chart from repo
helm install bravo bitnami/drupal 

> check chart
helm list

> uninstall chart from repo 
helm uninstall bravo bitnami/drupal 
helm list

> Download chart from existing repo
helm pull --untar bitnami/apache
